{"tid":1611042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗諗下其實係一早已經有預謀開真槍","createTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T01:54:36.000Z","uid":3351,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8517bba8252a336cbd4479b5f4b38861368cbf9e","tid":1611042,"uid":3351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:17.000Z","msg":"早一日記者會，盧狗出黎話有示威者想殺警<br />\n第二日警察就開真槍，話佢地受襲擊先開槍<br />\n其真一早舖好曬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c75df6bd09177f9971bd7975d83e03809693c0c","tid":1611042,"uid":254594,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8517bba8252a336cbd4479b5f4b38861368cbf9e","tid":1611042,"uid":3351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:17.000Z","msg":"早一日記者會，盧狗出黎話有示威者想殺警<br />\n第二日警察就開真槍，話佢地受襲擊先開槍<br />\n其真一早舖好曬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:49:28.000Z","msg":"&lt;這不是警察的自我防衛&gt;<br />\n肯定有很多人會這麼說，『示威者威脅到了警察的生命，所以警察開槍。』<br />\n<br />\n不，影片清晰可見，警察拿著左輪手槍的時候是往前行，而不是向後退，那不是自我防衛，那是攻擊的姿態，當你有著所有的武器，警棍，防暴槍那麼多選擇可以用的時候，卻選擇使用手槍，這不是自我防衛。<br />\n<br />\n開真槍這個行為，從警察開始稱呼人們為曱甴的時候我就知道遲早會發生，那是培養警察對人非人化的過程，培養警察對人產生恨意的過程，再加上假新聞，洗腦。連服從命令也不需要，他們自然而然的就已經對黑衣的示威者充滿著仇恨，這是我們的敵人，這是要謀害我們性命的人。<br />\n<br />\n所以這一下，是那個警察自己想做的。<br />\n<br />\n不要再出來行騙，到處幫他解釋他面對多少危險，他多害怕，所以才開槍，你的掩飾無恥得可笑，我卻笑不出。<br />\n<br />\n這是你們養出來的，殺人警察。"},{"pid":"536e14ffd221fbb6cd9720a7f4c65707497f167c","tid":1611042,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:50:48.000Z","msg":"一早有便衣著住避彈衣,重要係中共武警既"},{"pid":"06e1714e3942c51ff3016d84246ef8a473e860ba","tid":1611042,"uid":167956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"你見班魔警係主動衝出去進攻的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559743f21947e786e2495369853de1e00312d5e7","tid":1611042,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c7d9a5cc94fea9309456caefa5bb594648924e","tid":1611042,"uid":278723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:56:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得係日頭警力好少，啲狗成日做啲戇鳩野走去撩我哋將自己擺係一個弱勢，區區都係咁，然後等機會用真槍"},{"pid":"5cf006ccf7eb52124f57bb57b909d835fe03c360","tid":1611042,"uid":267680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:56:40.000Z","msg":"你估自衛開槍唔系8964咩"},{"pid":"85432f81d849a966a13b5705b5fccc1ff446f8e8","tid":1611042,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92987342aab9fbae40cf3294dcdbbfd6b6b5488c","tid":1611042,"uid":42978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"明顯係落咗order可以用，噚日開完咁快可以講晒大話掩飾就知"},{"pid":"1afd54ee3b868f3407ae4c35c4b07fcc2955fdd3","tid":1611042,"uid":307857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvq4GiD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftvq4GiD.jpg&h=ba4139eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jRb5Lj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jRb5Lj.jpg&h=1da9e9d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MVTzDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MVTzDF.jpg&h=16acb2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有公安兩點幾係屯門已經著左避彈衣</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b149babf8e42953b02e1977b500772564498c17a","tid":1611042,"uid":3351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92987342aab9fbae40cf3294dcdbbfd6b6b5488c","tid":1611042,"uid":42978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"明顯係落咗order可以用，噚日開完咁快可以講晒大話掩飾就知"},"citedBy":0,"repl